 # Expense Tracker

A command-line expense tracking application built with Python.

## Features
- Add expenses with category, amount, and note
- View all saved expenses
- Data stored persistently using JSON file

## Tech Stack
- Python
- JSON (file storage)
- OS module (file handling)

## How to Run
[8:23 pm, 08/06/2026] aptha: ## Usage
- Choose *1* to add an expense
- Choose *2* to view all expenses  
- Choose *3* to exit
